snippet.title: Best VGM 1317 - Mario Kart : Double Dash !! - Peach Beach & Daisy Cruiser
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 515 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QLsVsiWgTMo
Best VGM 2115 - https://youtu.be/y9SFrBt1xtw

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

Gamecube
Mario Kart: Double Dash!! (2003)
Peach Beach & Daisy Cruiser
Shinobu Tanaka / Kenta Nagata
